title: 12 of the Best and Funniest Women of 'SNL' (PHOTOS)
text:
start slideshow 
Women have always been a big part of Saturday Night Live. In fact the first person ever cast for the show was a woman, Gilda Radner. Since then some of its most successful performers have had boobs, including Kristen Wiig, Tina Fey, and Amy Poehler, to name just a few of SNL 's most memorable comediennes. 
Here are the 12 best female SNL cast members to ever don a wig, cheerleader outfit, or pair of frame-less glasses and make us ROTFL.
